file.name: openapi30.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: Spring Page/Pageable API
  version: 1.0.0

paths:
  /page:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: pageable
          required: false
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pageable'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: none
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/StringPage'

  /page-inline:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: pageable
          required: false
          schema:
            type: object
            properties:
              page:
                type: integer
              size:
                type: integer
      responses:
        '200':
          description: none
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                allOf:
                  - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Page'
                  - $ref: '#/components/schemas/StringContent'

components:
  schemas:

    Pageable:
      description: minimal Pageable query parameters
      type: object
      properties:
        page:
          type: integer
        size:
          type: integer

    Page:
      description: minimal Page response without content property
      type: object
      properties:
        number:
          type: integer
        size:
          type: integer

    StringContent:
      description: specific content List of the Page response
      type: object
      properties:
        content:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string

    StringPage:
      description: typed Page
      type: object
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Page'
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/StringContent'
